libspnav: libspnav is a free (BSD-licensed) alternative to the proprietary
libspnav: 3Dconnexion libraries for accessing 3D input devices such as the
libspnav: SpaceNavigator, SpaceMouse and similar 6-degrees-of-freedom (6dof)
libspnav: devices. It communicates with the spacenavd daemon and exposes a
libspnav: simple C API (spnav.h) for receiving motion and button events.
